# ? SwappedRows Pivot
GaussEliminate‼ ↚ ∧(
  ⊢⍖⊸⌵⍜⊙↙×0⟜⊡⤚⊸⊙⍉
  ⍜⊏⇌ ⊃⊙⊙∘^0 ⊟⤙⊙⊙∘ ⊙(⊃⋅⊙∘^1 ˙⍤≥ε⊸⌵) ⟜⊡
  ⊸⍜⊡(÷˜⊸⊡)⊸F
  ⍜(°⊂↻|˜⊙-˜⊸⊞×⊙(⊡⤚˜⊙⍉))⊸F
)°⊏

# Matrix Determinant
MDet ← ◌⍣GaussEliminate‼(⍥¯H!H!/≠)H!H!× ⊙0⊙1

# Perform Gauss-Jordan elimination
Mgje ← ⊏⍏˜⨂1>1e-12⊸⌵ ⍥(
  ↻₁⍣(⍜⊙⊢÷⟜(-⊞×⊙⊸⊢⊂0÷)°⊂⊸≡⊏⊢)◌⊚>1e-12⌵⊸⊢
)⊸⧻
# Mgje ← ⍣GaussEliminate‼(|)(⍤"Elimination cannot be completed"0)

# Matrix Inverse
MInv ← |1 ⌅(⍜⍉(↘÷2⊸⧻) ⍣Mgje(⍤"Matrix has no inverse"0) ˜≡⊂˙⊞=°⊏|MInv)

