# Rank-polymorphic convolution using fast fourier transform
┌─╴FFTConvolve
  # Full convolution wherever any overlap between the inputs exists
  Full ← ⍥R=0↥⊃∩type(×√/×⊸△⍜∩fft×∩⌞⬚0↙-1+◡∩△)
